hey race at speeds of up to 80 kph (50 mph).\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a harness\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"their boards\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"impossible angles\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"speeds\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 80 kph\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"50 mph\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attached to the board is a long keel with foil at the bottom which is what helps to lift the board out of the water.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"a long keel\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"foil\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They kites are steered with a control bar.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a control bar\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like other sailing events, kiteboarders race around buoys on a course, trying to avoid tangling with each others' strings or letting the huge, brightly coloured kites which power them dip into the water.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other sailing events\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"kiteboarders race\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"buoys\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"a course\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"each others' strings\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge, brightly coloured kites\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic equipment, Formula Kite, is 